<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">فِيهِ مَسَائِلُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الأُولَى:</span> الفَرْقُ بَينَ ذِمَّةِ اللهِ وَذِمَّةِ نَبِيِّهِ؛ وَذِمَّةِ المُسْلِمِينَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الثَّانِيَةُ:</span> الإِرْشَادُ إِلَى أَقَلِّ الأَمْرَينِ خَطَرًا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الثَّالِثَةُ:</span> قَولُهُ: <span class="c2">((اُغْزُوَا بِسْمِ اللهِ، فِي سَبِيلِ اللهِ)</span>).<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الرَّابِعَةُ:</span> قَولُهُ: <span class="c2">((قَاتِلُوا مَنْ كَفَرَ بِاللَّهِ)</span>).<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">الخَامِسَةُ:</span> قَولُهُ: <span class="c2">((اسْتَعِنْ بِاللَّهِ وَقَاتِلْهُمْ)</span>).<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">السَّادِسَةُ:</span> الفَرْقُ بَينَ حُكْمِ اللهِ وَحُكْمِ العُلَمَاءِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">السَّابِعَةُ:</span> فِي كَونِ الصَّحَابِيِّ يَحْكُمُ عِنْدَ الحَاجَةِ بِحُكْمٍ لَا يَدْرِي أَيُوَافِقُ حُكْمَ اللهِ أَمْ لَا؟<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>